Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 能用的水都用上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on! Let's use all the water we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点...用床单扑灭火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hurry up! Hurry up! Use sheets to put out the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这些棚屋拆掉 我们需要清出一条防火道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tear down these huts. We need to make a firebreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这些火 你想要杀了我 来呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hate these fires. You want to kill me? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么起火了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's burning?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是萨嘎尔瓦达 林之前住的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Sagar Wada. It's where Lin was staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说他已经离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said yourself he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 伤口要保持干净 明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. You have to keep this clean. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:01:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Understand. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林先生 愿和平与你同在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salaam alaikum, Mr. Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿和平与你同在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wa alaikumu assalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡西姆阿里 这里的村长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Qasim Ali, headman here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布和我说了很多你的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu has told me all about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for what you are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有更好的物资 我就能做更多事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I could do more with better supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能把所能找到的给我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you get me whatever you have--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有些人需要住院 药物 静脉注射\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some of these people need hospital, drugs, IVs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 但这里是弄不到那些东西的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, but none of these things will be coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有的都已经给你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You already have what we have, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕瓦蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Parvati?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能看看拉克什米吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can someone take a look at Lakshmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克什米 发生什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened? What happened, Lakshmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 快过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 把她扶到这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, bring her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再给我一张桌子 把她放平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need another table, to lie her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢一点 轻一点...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Slowly. Easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 你没事 对 你很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. You're all right. No, you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事的...慢慢来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're all right. Easy. You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问问她呼吸是否有困难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ask her if she's having trouble breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她需要去医院才能移除这金属\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She needs a hospital to take out that metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你做不到吗  -对 不可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, you can't do this? -No. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为那金属刺穿了她的肺部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's punctured her lung.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 -拉维\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom. -Ravi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No, no, no! It came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉维 -妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ravi! -Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布 用手按住 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu! Put your hands on there, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧地按压\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Solid pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手拿开...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move your hands. Move your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抱着她 可以吗  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to hold her. All right? -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让她移动 -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't let her move. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉她这能帮助她呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell her this is gonna help her breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get away from my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡西姆 太吵了 我听不见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Qasim, I need to be able to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉维 别这样 他是想救她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ravi, stop! He's trying to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉维 -可以吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ravi. -That good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉维... -妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ravi. Ravi. -Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉维\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ravi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的 见鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit. Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  -她必须立即看医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened? -She needs a doctor now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布 帮我将她抬起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu, help me lift her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数到三 一 二 三\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On three. One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 -林先生 你要带她去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom. -Mr. Lin, where are you taking her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她需要见医生 否则很快就会死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She needs a doctor, or she's gonna die quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让她死在所爱之人的环绕下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then let her die surrounded by the people she loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望她能在所爱之人的陪伴下生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want her to live with the people she loves,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在陪伴下死去 帕拉布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not die with them. Prabhu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不对的 -数到三 一 二 三\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is wrong. -On three. One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉维... -拉克什米 没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ravi. Ravi. -Lakshmi, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要带你去看医生 -快...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're taking you to the doctor. -Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉维...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ravi. Ravi! Ravi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 拉维 他们在救你的母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry, Ravi. They're helping your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布 她不能死 不能因我而死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's not dying, Prabhu. Not because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 帮帮我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey! We need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 停车 嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey! Stop! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布... -这里有位女人生命垂危\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu, Prabhu. -We got a dying woman here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu. Prabhu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿...停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 停下 够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin, stop! Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不重要了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It does not matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想见拉维\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She asked for Ravi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们很快就会回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多少个棚屋被烧毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many huts have burned?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30个 包括我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thirty. Mine included.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿点食物和奶茶 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will go get some food and chai, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不饿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经尽力做到最好 我清楚 所以你可以...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were trying to do the best thing. I know this. So you can--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布 要不是我在这里 根本就不会有这场火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu, if I hadn't been here, this fire would've never happened--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 拜托...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin, please. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里发生火灾并不奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fires, they happen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为拉克什米的死不让我难过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I'm not hating Lakshmi is gone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次我们已经算幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This time, we are lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年发生过一场更大的火灾 贫民区被烧毁的地方更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last year, there was much bigger fire, much more of the jhopadpatti was burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20多个人死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than 20 died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带点食物回来 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will bring food, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下...该死...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drop the-- Fuck. Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下剪贴板 举起双手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drop the clipboard and put your hands up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get the fuck on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰任何警报键 知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't touch any fucking alarm buttons, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几位女士 能把这些袋子装满吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could you ladies fill these bags up, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都有保险的 真的不用担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all insured. It's really not worth worrying about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照他说的做吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just do what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 劳拉 -好的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please... Laura. -Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懒惰的混蛋 为什么不找个工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you get a job, you lazy bastards?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 不好意思 这就是我们的工作 肥猪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey! Excuse me, this is our job, you fat ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挡我们的道 懂吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't get in the way of us doing it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 亲爱的 别担心 你只需要把袋子装满\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, love. It's all good. You just need to fill the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出来她很害怕吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't you see she's terrified?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把袋子装满\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just fill the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让一让...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out of the way! Out of the way! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 哥们 是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, mate. My fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 放开我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. Get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把枪放下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drop the bloody gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 混蛋 放下枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get off me! Bastard. Drop the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get the fuck off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把枪放下 快放下... -好...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drop the gun! Drop it! Drop it! -Okay. Okay. Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴尔 快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dale, fucking move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救护车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somebody, call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 嘿...保持清醒 嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Hey, hey. Stay with me. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会有事的 伙计 你没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're all right, mate. You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持清醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离他远点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿和平与你同在 瓦利德拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salaam alaikum, Walidbhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿和平与你同在 卡德尔拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alaikumu assalam, Khaderbhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方选得有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Interesting choice of location.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到过去的好日子里 多少人曾在这谋生 就感到难过啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sad to think how many men once earned a living here in better days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙计 一切事物都有使用期限 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arre, everything has its use-by date, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切人也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想聊聊 我们可以在这聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, you wanted to talk. This is where we can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁祖阿德卡死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rujul Aadekar is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是你 我也会做同样的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had I been in your shoes, I would have done exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有公司都处于和平状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the companies are at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的人没有在街上互相杀戮和开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our men are not killing and shooting each other in the streets,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都心满意足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and everyone is satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司之间很和平是因为 经营者都是些疲惫的老人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The companies are at peace because they're run by tired, old men
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安于现状\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who've settled for the status quo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Except yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Except mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁祖生前认为你软弱 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rujul, he believed you are weak, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道何为正确不意味着一个人软弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Certainty of what is right does not make anyone weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则经营克拉巴护照市场的 会是你 而不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or you'd still be running the passport market in Colaba, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦利德 是因为这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that what this is, Walid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为自尊心受伤 你想掀起战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want to start a war over your hurt pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算掀起任何东西 伙计 这只关乎生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not starting anything. This is business, yaar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨嘎尔瓦达价值连城 所以我不过是向鲁祖出了更高的价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sagar Wada is worth a fortune. So, I simply made Rujul a better offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会失去萨嘎尔瓦达的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am not going to lose Sagar Wada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是威胁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是简单陈述事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A simple statement of fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说是事实而已吧 大叔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For you maybe, chachu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个男人也许认为自己的老婆漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see, one man can say his wife is beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但另一个男人却觉得她丑陋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and another only sees a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我简单陈述事实的话 我的人手和金钱比你多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see, I think it is a simple fact that I have more men and money than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也认为女人和毒品生意才有未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it is a simple fact that women and drugs are the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而你选择留在过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and yet you choose to stay in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡德尔拜 你必须给人们他们想要的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to give the people what they want, Khaderbhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则你会成为历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Otherwise, you are consigned to history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我会在我的地盘 萨嘎尔瓦达的门前为你建一座大雕像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I'll build a big statue of you at the gates of my Sagar Wada, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你交谈总是很愉快 瓦利德拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Always a pleasure talking with you, Walidbhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了 太好了 跟我来 有个东西你必须看看 老大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're awake? Good. Come. Something you gotta see, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 稍等片刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Just give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊 哥们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come, na.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are they all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是你的病人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're your patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都知道你昨晚治疗居民的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They all know about the doctoring you did last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在排队来看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so now they wait to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...我可不是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No. I'm not--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 不会有问题的 林先生 -我不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin, no-- no problem waiting, Linbaba. -I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:15:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经等了一个多小时了 我说你得睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're here more than one hour already. I told them you must sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你没来 他们也会继续等的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if you were not here, they would still be waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是白等一场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but waiting for nothing only.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会让他们失去希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that kills the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是等待有所回报 那就不同了 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But waiting for something, that is different, na?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能这么做 听着 我都不算医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't do that. Look, I'm not even a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕的医生总比没医生好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even bad doctor better than no doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说你糟糕 意思是即使你糟糕也没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not saying you are bad, only that if you were, it would be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布 -拉克什米原本就无法生还的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu. -Lakshmi was going to die anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会为她悼念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we will grieve her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有时生活就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that is how it is sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布 你好吗  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you, Prabhu? -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 关于昨晚 我想道歉 你是对的 我应该听你的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I wanna say sorry about last night. You were right. I should have listened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡西姆 他会帮我们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Qasim, is he going to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没这么想逃跑过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to run more than ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用卡拉的钱赋予我的第二次机会 就此离开孟买\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}take the second chance Karla's money had given me and get out of Bombay,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我接受的帮助令这些人蒙受痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}despite what helping me had done to these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很好的 相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will be good, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God willing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林先生 这笔钱不少啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a lot of money to be giving away, Linbaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我需要的东西也不少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, I'm gonna need a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你为什么要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But why you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有我的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got my reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 收下 用这笔钱重建烧毁的屋子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on, take it. Use it to rebuild the homes that burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会确保每分每毫都用在对的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will make sure every paisa is well spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 再等两分钟 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right! Just two more minutes. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涂抹一点这个 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put some of this on, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只可能是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It had to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受过相同培训的人 不会因为犯罪而被迫躲在贫民区里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another man with my training wouldn't have been forced by crime into the slum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而罪犯不会像我一样接受过医疗培训\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another criminal wouldn't have had my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂当中的幽默 我也不觉得这命运好笑在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't get the joke, and fate didn't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道我不能离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I knew I couldn't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有20个病人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have 20 more patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 出来 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay? Out. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得吃点东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐可真是丰盛啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Breakfast of champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有时候真幼稚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can be such a child sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是因为我帮你戒毒而生我气吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you angry with me for helping you get clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气的人是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the one who's angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是要照顾我这点让你这么生气吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does it piss you off so much that you have to look after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能照顾好自己 莉莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to look after yourself, Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不会的 因为你就喜欢自己孱弱无力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you won't, because you like being powerless,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为无论你身处哪一个宇宙 这让你成为那里的中心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because it makes you the center of whatever universe you happen to be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人照顾他人是出于爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some people look after you because they love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是坏事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那人离开了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what happens when they aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能一辈子拒绝关心某人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't spend your life refusing to care for anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因他们可能离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in case they leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎 我不能和你吵 现在不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't do this, Lisa. Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的情况下 我不想和你争执\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't wanna fight with you, not with everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对 我的表现太自私 像个被宠坏的贱人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're right. I'm being a selfish, spoiled bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我满脑子都在想不能软弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yesterday, all I could think about was not being weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我一闭眼 只看到死去的鲁祖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now, I close my eyes, and all I see is Rujul dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡达尔知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Khader knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想保护我 但他做得越多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He tried to protect me, and the more he did,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就越是坚定地想要证明自己能应对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the more I was determined to prove myself I could handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉 你不需要证明任何事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to prove anything, Karla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不那么做 交易会失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I don't, the deal will fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有多糟呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And would that be so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次任自己放松 感到快乐 是什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When is the last time you let yourself go and felt happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Truly happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起当废物吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's be fucked-up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证会吃一些 不对你犯浑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promise to eat some of this and not be a royal pain in the ass,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你保证留在这陪我 和我一起听唱片 像旧日一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you promise to stay here with me and play records with me like old times
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我们喝光了酒 嗑完了大麻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until we run out of booze and hash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要休息 我可以让他们明天再来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are needing rest? I can tell them to come back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 林医生要休息一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop! Dr. Lin will be taking a break now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给你的谢礼 林医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a thank-you, Dr. Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这是帕拉布的主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it was actually Prabhu's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说服卡西姆阿里这么做 让我用他的棚屋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He talked Qasim Ali into it and let me use his hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我说服卡西姆阿里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I talked Qasim Ali into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是帕拉布买来了所有这些物资\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was Prabhu who got all the supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物资是我买的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got the supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布 你这么做真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu, this was a good thing that you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要帮忙照料病人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need help with patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我们可以的 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. We're good, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个很好吃啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is great, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林先生 不错吧 非常顺利...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very good, huh, Linbaba? Very slick, very smooth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你让她走 帕瓦蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until you sent her away. Parvati!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想的话 吃完后 我可以把盘子送还你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you like, I will bring back your tray when we are finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去奶茶店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At the chai shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会在那里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 你们看什么呢 你们没正事干吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, what are you staring at? Haven't you got work to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得有滋有味啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are enjoying, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美味...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yummy, yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫殿的营运模式是预约制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Palace operates on an appointment-only basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫殿营运是因为我们允许它营运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Palace operates because we let it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉周说我们到了 去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell Zhou we're here. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕德玛 我不是某个无助的女孩 会屈从你们的规矩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not some helpless girl, Padma, that will bend to your discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须把携带的武器留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will need to leave any weapons you carry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.78,0:23:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.88,0:23:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡德尔拜 太荣幸了 请问需要什么喝的或吃的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is an honor, Khaderbhai. Can I get you something to drink or eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.68,0:23:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我与鲁祖阿德卡 进行了非常严肃的会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Recently, I spent a solemn moment with Rujul Aadekar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晨我和瓦利德沙会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This morning, I spent some time with Walid Shah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我来看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now, I've come to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不赞许你做的生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not approve of your business,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.99,0:24:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我理解这种生意必定会存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I understand it is a business that must exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你被允许来这里 蓬勃发展\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you've been allowed to come here and prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.20,0:24:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的成功基于一个条件 就是中立\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there has been one condition to your success. Neutrality.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.33,0:24:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我犯了一个错 卡德尔拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made a mistake, Khaderbhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.21,0:24:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can only apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.59,0:24:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我以为你知悉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At first, I assumed you knew of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.55,0:24:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我意识到并非如此时 已经太晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I realized this wasn't the case, it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.14,0:24:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你说 我在孟买本地的处境脆弱...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you say, my position here in Bombay is vulnerable--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.69,0:24:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士 你不太擅长扮演受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You do not play the victim well, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你从前当情妇和妓女时 假装的功力更强一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you were better at faking back when you were a mistress and a whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.40,0:24:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我说的 我犯了一个错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like I said, I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.78,0:24:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我要为此死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if I was going to die for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.99,0:25:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为你不会亲自来这里动手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think you would come here yourself to watch it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.79,0:25:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去的你对我毫无用处 活着的你也许有些用处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dead, you are of no use to me. Alive, maybe I could use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.67,0:25:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应明白 当我离开这地方时 我会带上你的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Understand that when I leave this place, I will take your life with me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.84,0:25:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为你现在所欠债务的抵押品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as collateral against the debt that you now owe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.35,0:25:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我向你提出要求 你必须满足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when I ask something of you, you will do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.18,0:25:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则这地方会成为你的葬身殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or this place will burn as your funeral pyre.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.69,0:25:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.98,0:25:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡拉萨兰恩说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was it Karla Saaranen?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.74,0:25:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.61,0:25:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没听过这名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not know that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.28,0:25:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁祖是我的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rujul belonged to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.29,0:25:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对他的了解胜过他对自己的了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew him better than he knew himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.33,0:25:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我派人跟踪他 他去过哪里 做了什么 见了谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I had him followed, where he went, what he did, who he saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.92,0:25:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没想到这一点是他愚蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was stupid to think otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.67,0:25:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他的愚蠢让他送命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was his stupidity that got him killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.63,0:25:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你并不愚蠢 女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you're not stupid, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.55,0:26:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林先生 我们要为拉克什米的葬礼造柴堆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Linbaba, we are now going to build the pyre for Lakshmi's funeral
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.14,0:26:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你一起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you want to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.72,0:26:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 强尼 我没资格去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, Johnny. I got no right to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.31,0:26:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布说你责怪自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu told me you blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.19,0:26:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布话太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu talks too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.82,0:26:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.61,0:27:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡德尔拜今天饶了你一命 这么做明智吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Khaderbhai gave you your life today. Is this wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.95,0:27:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的命不由任何人赐予或拿走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My life isn't any man's to give or take.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.70,0:27:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他们一样了解他们的生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know their business as well as them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.25,0:27:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些“大哥”...去他们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All these bhais... Fuck them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.25,0:27:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是时候让位给“大姐”了 帕德玛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe it's time for the behains, Padma.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.71,0:27:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间有协定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We had a deal, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.43,0:28:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你说的是莉莎 我遵从了协定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're talking about Lisa, I kept my part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.26,0:28:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lisa is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.31,0:28:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为那是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't see how that is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.85,0:28:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛里齐奥 那你在怕什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why are you scared, Maurizio?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.64,0:28:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.65,0:28:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为你怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.57,0:28:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为只有这种时候 男人和女人才能真正一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think maybe it's the only time when men and women can truly be the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.16,0:28:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他们无权无势 害怕至极时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when they're powerless and terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.91,0:28:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是女人被迫拥有这种感受的时刻 比男人多得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But women are forced to feel it so much more than men.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.16,0:28:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往往是被男人逼迫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By men, usually.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.33,0:28:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么叫我来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.46,0:28:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得到我的原谅 有一个办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a way for you to earn my forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.84,0:28:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.01,0:28:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要你在克拉巴帮我卖海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to sell brown sugar for me in Colaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.89,0:28:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉巴是卡德尔拜的地盘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Colaba is Khaderbhai's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.77,0:28:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不在那里卖海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he doesn't sell heroin there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.15,0:28:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neither does anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.73,0:28:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对他并没有忠诚 你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I owe him no loyalty. Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.57,0:28:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.07,0:29:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对任何人都没有忠诚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I owe loyalty to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.53,0:29:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少这是大实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is honest, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.49,0:29:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的条件很简单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My terms are simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.49,0:29:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得提我的名字 你抽二成利润\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name is never mentioned. You keep 20% of the profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.50,0:29:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四成 风险全由我承担\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forty. I'm taking all of the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.75,0:29:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在和你磋商\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not negotiating with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.84,0:29:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much are we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.64,0:29:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能卖多少 我就有多少阿富汗海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have access to as much Afghan dope as you can sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.56,0:29:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 说定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay then. You have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.06,0:29:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就不需要害怕任何事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you have nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.69,0:29:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Lin?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.29,0:29:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫阿卜杜拉塔哈利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name's Abdullah Taheri.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.41,0:29:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个人想见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have someone who wants to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.58,0:29:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.67,0:30:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.02,0:30:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林赛福特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Lindsay Ford?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.02,0:30:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我林就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just "Lin" works.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.69,0:30:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你很高兴 久仰大名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm pleased to meet you. I've heard good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.36,0:30:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在孟买这里听到关于外国人的好话 总是令人开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's always nice to hear good things about foreigners here in Bombay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.24,0:30:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你也听过我 我是阿布戴尔卡达尔可汗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You might have heard of me also. My name is Abdel Khader Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.04,0:30:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在是棚屋区医生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you are the doctor in the hutments now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.46,0:30:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 我...距离医生还远着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm-- I'm a long way from being a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.17,0:30:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许正是因此你才这么出色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, maybe that is why you are doing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.38,0:30:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生不会主动来贫民区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doctors do not go into the jhopadpatti willingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.30,0:30:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以说服人不做坏事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can compel men not to be bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.14,0:30:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们无法说服他们做好事 你不觉得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we cannot compel them to do good, don't you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.73,0:30:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没思考过这点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never really thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.81,0:31:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什么东西能说服你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wonder what compels you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.78,0:31:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么能帮你的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there something I can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.57,0:31:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.86,0:31:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is why I am here,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.20,0:31:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请你和我的朋友阿卜杜拉聊聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to invite you to spend some time with me and my friend Abdullah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.75,0:31:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我无意冒犯 但是我就直说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. I mean no offense, but I'm just gonna say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.09,0:31:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名声挺吓人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a fairly scary reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.05,0:31:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你突然这样出现 应该不难理解我有点紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you just turning up like this, you can see why I might be a bit nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.93,0:31:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太想坐上你车的后座 让你载我走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about jumping in the back of your car and letting you drive me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.10,0:31:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证 今晚你不会受到任何伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I give you my word. No harm will come to you this night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.18,0:31:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有选择吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do I have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.35,0:31:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永远都有选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You always have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.31,0:31:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终 我认为选择是我们唯一拥有的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the end, I think that is all we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.20,0:31:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.82,0:32:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宵禁就像不存在一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So much for curfew.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.24,0:32:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当局知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The authorities know
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.66,0:32:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大城市的文明人需要聚会和谋生的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that civilized people in large cities need places to gather and hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.12,0:32:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以某些地方可以行贿 秩序得以被保留\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So certain establishments are permitted to pay a bribe, and order is preserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.00,0:32:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明面上法律依然有效 但不会执行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Officially, the law remains. It's just not enforced.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.59,0:32:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁决定哪些法律要执行 哪些法律不执行呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who gets to decide which laws get enforced and which ones don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.64,0:32:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人曾说腐败作为管治系统的一部分 最糟糕的一点在于\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone once said the worst thing about corruption as a system of governance
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.14,0:32:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的效果太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is that it works so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.60,0:33:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ramesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.11,0:33:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲可好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.57,0:33:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很好 卡德尔拜 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is well, Khaderbhai. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.20,0:33:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我遇到了麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I am having a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.62,0:33:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.75,0:33:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 是关于我的房东\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bhai, it's about my landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.33,0:33:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经要求租金涨一倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is demanding double rent already.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.46,0:33:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想驱逐我们 不只是我 还有楼里的所有家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants to evict us, not just me, but all the families in my building.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.92,0:33:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有打手 他的打手把我们打得很惨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has goondas, and his goondas beat us badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.51,0:33:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至包括我的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even my own father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.18,0:33:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你父亲并不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then he is not well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.64,0:33:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 先生 他的自尊心太强 不愿向你求助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, sir. He is too proud to ask you for help
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.94,0:33:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想打扰你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and doesn't want to disturb your peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.35,0:33:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.06,0:33:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个好儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a good son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.53,0:33:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会做任何伤害他自尊心的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We won't do anything to hurt his pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.90,0:33:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也毋须和你父亲提及这次谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And there will be no need to speak to your father about this
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.66,0:33:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到这个麻烦解决 愿上帝保佑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until the problem is solved, inshallah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.74,0:33:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你... -好的 是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, thank-- -Okay, okay. Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.62,0:34:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听懂了多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much did you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.62,0:34:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没多少 关于他家和他父亲什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not much. Something about his home and his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.34,0:34:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的房东想赶走他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their landlord wants them out of their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.80,0:34:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必要时会动粗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By force, if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.47,0:34:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你去威胁那个威胁他们的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you threaten the man who threatens them?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.14,0:34:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赞同吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you approve?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.72,0:34:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你并不需要我的赞同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think you need my approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.73,0:34:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是阿布戴尔卡达尔可汗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're Abdel Khader Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.19,0:34:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因为我可以轻易做某事 不意味着我应该这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just because I can easily do something doesn't always mean I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.82,0:34:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果换做是你 你觉得应该这样做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Humor me. If it were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.20,0:34:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得如果我喜欢拉米什 而这个房东的做法很过分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think if I liked Ramesh and this landlord was out of line,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.95,0:34:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我会尽我所能帮助他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then I'd do what I could for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.66,0:34:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那可能违法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if it meant acting against the law?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.16,0:34:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁决定哪些法律要执行 哪些法律不执行呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who gets to choose which laws get enforced and which ones don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.75,0:34:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终 无论是哪条法律 无论是谁来选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the end, regardless of laws or who chooses,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.76,0:35:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们每一个人 每个宇宙 每个星系中的每个原子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}each one of us, every atom in every galaxy in every universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.18,0:35:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会向上帝靠近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is moving towards God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.89,0:35:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不信上帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.77,0:35:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们能聊的就更多了 你和我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we have much more to talk about, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.36,0:35:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 我们带他去俱乐部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go. We will take him to the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.63,0:35:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了会陪我 -不 我只是没说不会陪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said you'd stay with me. -No. I just didn't say I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.84,0:35:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的协定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.05,0:35:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎 我已经走到这一步 我没有选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've come too far, Lisa. I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.89,0:35:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能让卡达尔可汗先生失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't disappoint Mr. Khader Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.81,0:35:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下 求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.48,0:35:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.57,0:35:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看出这给你带来的影响 你也知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can see what this is doing to you. You know it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.78,0:35:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是不愿承认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just won't admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.57,0:36:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择我 陪着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Choose me. Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.70,0:36:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这才是最重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because this matters the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.96,0:36:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在乎你 你清楚的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I care about you. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.63,0:36:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你还是要选他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're choosing him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.93,0:37:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家俱乐部有孟买最棒的加扎勒歌手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This club has the best ghazel singers in Bombay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.10,0:37:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是加扎勒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are ghazels?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.40,0:37:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱之曲 给上帝的爱之曲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Love songs. Love songs to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.57,0:37:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你怎么想 信上帝这件事并不存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter what you might think, there is no believing in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.86,0:37:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认识上帝 或不认识 只有这两种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We either know him or we do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.95,0:37:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识上帝 但我觉得 他的存在不太可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't know God, but I think he's pretty much impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.71,0:37:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝的存在不太可能正是他存在的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fact that God is impossible is proof he exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.75,0:37:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是不是所有可能的事物都不存在呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So does that mean that all possible things don't exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.17,0:37:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴你理解我的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm delighted you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.05,0:37:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.88,0:37:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友 你有麻烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're in trouble now, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.59,0:37:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何事物是我们所看到的样子 我们的眼睛是骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing exists as we see it. Our eyes are liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.22,0:37:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切看上去真实的东西都属于某种幻象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything that seems real is part of the illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.23,0:37:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 我 这个房间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You, me, this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.69,0:37:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么如果一切都是幻象 那我们怎么知道做什么 如何生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So if everything's an illusion, how do we know what to do, how to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.65,0:38:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.82,0:38:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑清醒的人不过是比 头脑不清醒的人更擅长说谎罢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The sane man is simply a better liar than the insane man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.57,0:38:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛会说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your eyes lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.24,0:38:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为自己知道的事情 让你认为并非如此 那其实这是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you think you know tells you this is not so, but it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.62,0:38:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们更喜欢谎言 因为那样更简单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We prefer the lie because it's easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.79,0:38:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要如何保持清醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's how we stay sane?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.09,0:38:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有结婚 我没有儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am not married, and I have no sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.64,0:38:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我告诉你 我清楚地看到你是我的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if I tell you that I see it clearly that you are my son,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.60,0:38:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卜杜拉是你的哥哥 我是你的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abdullah is your brother, I am your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.81,0:38:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会认为这不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you will think that is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.39,0:38:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会抗拒 你确实如此 我看得出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will resist it. You do. I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.57,0:38:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你宁肯相信我们都是陌生人这个谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You prefer to believe the lie that we are all strangers,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.36,0:38:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我们之间没有关连\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and there is no connection between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.57,0:38:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.20,0:38:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不了解你 你不了解我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I don't know you. You don't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.50,0:38:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think maybe I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.50,0:39:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林先生 你会对自己说哪些谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you lie to yourself about, Mr. Lin?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.84,0:39:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会 我已经不再那样做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't. I'm finished with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.93,0:39:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己是谁 做了什么 欠了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what I am, what I've done, what I owe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.27,0:39:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定喜欢林这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.95,0:42:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这音乐如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you like the music?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.53,0:43:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒极了 从没听过这样的音乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's incredible. I never heard anything like it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.12,0:43:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能问你一件事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.08,0:43:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的所有这些...你为什么带我来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All this, tonight... Why'd you bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.67,0:43:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想在我这里得到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.67,0:43:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.97,0:43:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听音乐 喝茶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listening, drinking tea,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.05,0:43:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习我所知道的世界是一种幻象这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}learning that the world as I know it is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.72,0:43:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗑嗨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm pretty stoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.14,0:43:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本应离开孟买的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were meant to leave Bombay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.31,0:43:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林先生 你的这位朋友是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is your friend, Mr. Lin?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.02,0:43:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是卡拉萨兰恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Karla Saaranen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.94,0:43:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.78,0:43:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.57,0:43:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说吧 到目前我在孟买的日子里 卡拉是重要而关键的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's just say Karla has had a full and central part of my life in Bombay so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.62,0:43:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是真是假\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Real or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.70,0:43:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得她是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think she's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.46,0:43:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.33,0:43:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉证明了我是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Karla proves that I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.34,0:43:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我想象出了她 她对我的态度应该好得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I invented her, she would be a lot nicer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.71,0:43:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉 这位是阿卜杜拉塔哈利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Karla, allow me to introduce Abdullah Taheri,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.18,0:44:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎是我没有血缘关系的兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my brother from another mother, apparently,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.18,0:44:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的新相识阿布戴尔卡达尔可汗先生 让我们两兄弟再聚首\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}recently reunited by my newest acquaintance, Mr. Abdel Khader Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.77,0:44:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大概听过他的大名 -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've probably heard of him. -Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.89,0:44:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉恩女士 幸会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a pleasure to meet you, Ms. Saaranen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.19,0:44:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此 你们是怎么认识的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Likewise. How do you all come to know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.23,0:44:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运使然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fate saw fit to throw us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.19,0:44:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Funny how that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.28,0:44:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 “处于苦难中的人不择伙伴”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, "Misery acquaints a man with strange bedfellows."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.53,0:44:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's the monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.66,0:44:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.91,0:44:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话是一个和怪物同床的人说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That line is spoken by a man who lies down with a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.50,0:44:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨兰恩女士对莎士比亚很了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ms. Saaranen knows her Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.42,0:44:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人曾告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone once told me
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.50,0:44:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生中的所有问题和大部分答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that all the questions and most of the answers in life
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.25,0:44:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都可以在莎士比亚里找到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can be found in Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.05,0:44:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加入我们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you like to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.67,0:44:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我还有客人要招待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't. I've got guests of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.84,0:44:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要谈生意 我应该回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have business to conclude. I should get back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.93,0:44:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你的生意顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good luck with your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.27,0:44:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿上帝保佑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inshallah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.85,0:44:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们今晚愉快 先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enjoy the rest of your evening, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.55,0:46:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 今晚很愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has been a pleasure, Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.10,0:46:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是某种考验吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was this some kind of test?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.68,0:46:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么在萨嘎尔瓦达帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do you help in Sagar Wada?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.90,0:46:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.48,0:46:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算是某种高尚举动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An act of nobility then?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.40,0:46:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 高尚这个词用不到我身上 这我可以打包票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nah, there's nothing noble about me. You can trust me on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.40,0:46:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人没有好坏之分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are no good men or bad men.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.66,0:46:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们做的事或不愿做的事 定义了他们的好坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is what they do, or refuse to do, that makes them good or evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.20,0:46:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方对我的意义重大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This place means a great deal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.88,0:46:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可汗先生 多谢你今晚的招待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for tonight, Mr. Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.05,0:46:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我卡德尔拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, call me Khaderbhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.72,0:46:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡德尔拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Khaderbhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.85,0:46:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发音还算标准\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.98,0:47:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是命运 让我和这两个人相遇 父亲和兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe fate brought me together with these men, father and brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.48,0:47:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那之后发生的一切都是我自己的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But everything that came after was down to my own choices,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.53,0:47:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如卡达尔说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just like Khader had said.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.74,0:48:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了她 你杀了我的母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You took her away. You took my mother away.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.95,0:48:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的全部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was all I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.75,0:48:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.88,0:48:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是无心之失 但的确如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't mean to, but I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.80,0:48:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉维 我受够了永远做错事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm tired, Ravi, of getting it so fucking wrong all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.76,0:48:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要用这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you gonna use that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.35,0:49:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉维\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ravi!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.98,0:49:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉维 你在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing, Ravi?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.19,0:49:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉维 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ravi, my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.36,0:49:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲已经离世\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your mother is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.66,0:49:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做 你也会毁了自己的一辈子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do this, and you'll lose yourself forever also.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.62,0:49:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.50,0:49:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子不应该\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This child does not deserve
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.96,0:49:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为杀了你而背负良心的重担 林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to carry your murder on his conscience, Mr. Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.75,0:49:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂这一点说明你是个自私的傻瓜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you are a selfish fool for not knowing better.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.47,0:49:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去我的棚屋 你和我家人一起生活吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to my hut. You will stay with my family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.31,0:49:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 卡西姆叔叔 拜托 我不伤他 但...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Uncle Qasim, please. I won't hurt him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.14,0:49:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉维 听我的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ravi. Do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.31,0:49:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.32,0:49:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对他说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you say to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.45,0:49:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在和我家人一起生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That he will stay with my family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.66,0:49:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克什米的棚屋属于你了 林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lakshmi's hut will now be yours, Mr. Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.41,0:50:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人需要你的帮助时 就会来这里找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When people here need your help, this is where they will find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.00,0:50:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我给你的礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not a gift I'm giving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.76,0:50:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
